t=Gayer|first=Laurent|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=BklRBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA156&lpg=PA156&dq=karachi+towns+disbanded+2011&source=bl&ots=a0EX8EYYqr&sig=ACfU3U1ZiUfKRKtF9CzZQ7yMEaA8aAfgPg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwir4qiZ--3oAhXjK30KHRWgDCsQ6AEwAnoECA8QKA#v=onepage&q=karachi%20towns%20disbanded%202011&f=false|title=Karachi: Ordered Disorder and the Struggle for the City|date=2014|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-0-19-935444-3|language=en}}</ref> and Baldia Town was re-organized as part of [[Karachi West]] in 2015.  \n\n== Location ==\nIt was bordered by [[SITE Town]] and [[Orangi]] to the east and by [[Kiamari Town]] to the north and west, with most of the western boundary formed by part of the [[RCD Highway]]. \n\n== Neighbourhoods ==\n<br />\n\n* [[Abidabad]]\n* [[Afridi Colony]]\n* [[Bismillah Chowk]]\n* [[Kumhar Colony]]\n* [[Delhi Colony]] \n* [[Dhoraji Colony]]\n* [[Gujrat Colony]] \n* [[Gulshan-e-Ghazi]]\n* [[Islamnagar (Karachi)|Islamnagar]]\n* [[Ittehad Town]]\n* [[Kokan Colony]]\n* [[Muhajir Camp]]\n* [[Muslim Mujahid Colony]]\n* [[Nai Abadi]]\n* [[Naval Colony]]\n* [[Rasheedabad]]\n* [[Saeedabad, Karachi|Saeedabad]]\n* [[Kumhar colony]]\n* [[dawood wachani goth sector 17]] \n\n== See also ==\n* [[City District Government]]\n* [[Karachi]]\n* [[Lahore]]\n* [[Veraval Turk Jamaat]]\n* [[Mutahid Muslim Kutchi Kumhar Jammat rgst]]\n* [[All Baldia Town Patni muslim Jamaat RGST]]\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.karachicity.gov.pk Official Karachi website]\n\n{{Karachi Towns}}\n{{Karachi topics}}\n\n{{coord|24|55|28|N|66|58|25|E|display=title|region:PK_type:city_source:GNS-enwiki}}\n\n[[Category:Baldia Town| ]]\n\n\n{{Karachi-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n<!-- Basic info  ---------------->| name                            = Baldia Town<br>{{nq|\u0628\u0644\u062f\u06cc\u06c1 \u0679\u0627\u0624\u0646}}\n| settlement_type                 = [[Towns in Karachi|Constituent Town of Karachi]]\n<!-- images and maps  ----------->| image_skyline                   = \n| image_caption                   = \n| image_flag                      = \n| image_seal                      = \n| image_map                       = Baldia Town Karachi.PNG\n| map_caption                     = Baldia Town was divided into 8 Union Councils\n<!-- Location ------------------>| subdivision_type                = Country\n| subdivision_name                = [[Pakistan]]\n| subdivision_type1               = Province\n| subdivision_name1               = [[Sindh]]\n| subdivision_type2               = City District\n| subdivision_name2               = [[Karachi, Sindh, Pakistan]]\n| parts_type                      = Union Councils\n| parts_style                     = list, coll\n| parts                           = 8\n| p1                              = [[Ittehad Town]]<br>[[Gulshan-e-Ghazi]]<br>[[Islamnagar (Karachi)|Islam Nagar]]<br>[[Muhajir Camp]]<br>[[Muslim Mujahid Colony]]<br>[[Nai Abadi]]<br>[[Rasheedabad]]<br> [[Saeedabad, Karachi|Saeedabad]]\n<!-- Politics ----------------->| government_footnotes            = \n| government_type                 = Town Council\n| leader_title1                   = Constituency\n| leader_name1                    = [[NA-249 (Karachi West-II)]]\n| leader_title2                   = National Assembly Member\n| leader_name2                    = [[Faisal Vawda]] ([[Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf|PTI]])\n| established_title               = Established\n| established_date                = August 2011\n| area_magnitude                  = 1 E+6\n| area_footnotes                  = \n| area_total_km2                  = \n| area_total_sq_mi                = <!-- Elevation -------------------------->\n| elevation_footnotes             = \n| elevation_m                     = \n| elevation_ft                    = <!-- Population   ----------------------->\n| population_as_of                = 1998\n| population_footnotes            = \n